name: SafeZone
0:
”Alexa, ask safe zone How safe is the city of Irvine?”
”How safe is the neighborhood of Los Angeles?”
”What is the safety rating for the Los Angeles area?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: safe zone
des: This skill enables Alexa to provide the Safety Rating of a city.This skill can be used by travelers visiting a new city or planning to visit a new city.It can be used by parents to determine if their children are in a safe city.
